    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This car is a good, well-kept example that presents nicely overall and should make a solid driver for its next owner. It appears clean and complete, with a tidy exterior, a respectable interior, and the kind of overall condition you would expect from a vehicle that has been used but cared for over time. It is not a mint, show-level car, so buyers should expect some normal cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections, but nothing that takes away from it being an attractive and usable vehicle. Overall, this is an honest good-condition car for someone who wants a nice example they can enjoy without paying top-tier money.",
