      "description": "A classic with real vintage charm and a lot to like for someone who appreciates an honest car. It presents decently, is enjoyable as a driver, and offers a solid foundation for light improvement over time. Not a showpiece, but a straightforward, appealing classic with character that can be enjoyed as-is while you continue to sort and refresh it.",
