      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. This vehicle shows its age but remains a practical option for someone looking for a budget-friendly daily driver, backup car, or project. A great chance to get into a vehicle at an accessible price point without overpaying.",
      "price": 6950.0,
