    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants cheap transportation, a handy backup car, or a fun little project. It starts, runs, and gives you a lot of value for the money, and I\u2019m listing it honestly so there are no surprises. If you want something inexpensive and usable without spending a fortune, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, straightforward driver with strong project potential. Starts, runs, and moves, with a powertrain that feels mechanically serviceable and a chassis that offers a solid foundation for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. Not a show car, but a usable platform with honest wear and the kind of simplicity that makes it appealing as a budget commuter, weekend fixer, or parts-saver candidate. If you want an inexpensive entry point and don\u2019t mind giving it the cosmetic and deferred-attention items it deserves, this one has real upside.",
      "price": 5900.0,
